Global Pet Food Processing Machinery Market Insights
Pet Food Processing Machinery Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Pet Food Processing Machinery Market Overview
The global pet food processing machinery market was valued at approximately USD 8.6 billion in 2023 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 5.4% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for high-quality, nutritious pet food and the continuous innovation in food processing technologies. Factors such as the growing pet adoption rates globally and an expanding focus on premium, organic, and natural pet foods are contributing to the rise in market value. The market includes equipment for processing dry and wet pet food, as well as specialized machinery for food formulation, mixing, and packaging. Demand for more sustainable and efficient processing machinery also plays a key role in market expansion.

